  - m_Id: 58454958080
    m_Localized: Let's see if there's any mail in my inbox...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1567905275904
    m_Localized: 'Oh my! They hacked my PC! It''s full of bugs!!! '
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2178537218048
    m_Localized: I have to go rewire the circuits!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5540578058240
    m_Localized: HERE IT IS! THE LATEST BUG!!!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5951758262272
    m_Localized: 'You won''t escape me: The power of debugging!!!'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 6270198210560
    m_Localized: Hurray! The computer is safe!!!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 6625543839744
    m_Localized: The End.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3988544056975360
    m_Localized: You can now rotate blocks with R!
